songs.title: SIN JAALLADHAA
songs.lyrics:
Akka eenyuufuu miti akka keefan jiraadhee Dhugaadha 
 Silaa yoona du'ee eddoon awwaalcha koyyuu onaadha 
 Biyya lafaa beeka na wajjin waan baayee dbarsitee 
 Ana nama deegaa si jaalla waanjoo koo caccabsitee 

 Sin jaalladhaa Ani Sin Jaalladha 
 Baayeen si Jaalladha Baayee Baayee
 Yesuus Sin Jaalladha akka eenyuufuu miti akka keefan jiraadhee Dhugaadha 
 silaa yoona du'ee eddoon awwaalcha koyyuu onaadha 
 Biyya lafaa beeka na wajjin waan baayee dbarsitee 
 ana nama deegaa si jaalla waanjoo koo caccabsitee 

 sin jaalladhaa
